==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undistinctive
<hw>Un`dis*tinc"tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Making no
distinctions; not discriminating; impartial.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As <qex>undistinctive</qex> Death will come here one day.</q>
<rj><qau>Dickens.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undistinctly</ent>⟦br⟧
